headline: Expeditors International (EXPD): Exploring Valuation as Analyst Optimism Grows Ahead of Upcoming Earnings Release
summary: Expeditors International of Washington (EXPD) has been attracting investor interest because of its record of outperforming earnings estimates over the last two quarters. Analysts are now watching for the next report in early November. See our latest analysis for Expeditors International of Washington. Expeditors International’s share price has rebounded in recent weeks, rising 7.4% over the past 90 days and recapturing ground lost earlier this quarter. Despite muted total shareholder return...
